♪You made it through the worst♪

1091
00:49:52,082 --> 00:49:54,160
♪The best is yet to come♪

1092
00:49:54,409 --> 00:49:56,579
♪The best is yet to come♪

1093
00:49:59,280 --> 00:50:00,432
♪Isn't it magical♪

1094
00:50:00,432 --> 00:50:04,078
♪All the stars are out tonight♪

1095
00:50:04,112 --> 00:50:05,968
♪And I see them sparkling♪

1096
00:50:06,192 --> 00:50:08,323
♪Nobody knows♪

1097
00:50:08,944 --> 00:50:10,854
♪What tomorrow brings♪

1098
00:50:11,120 --> 00:50:13,443
♪You made it through the worst♪

1099
00:50:13,630 --> 00:50:15,838
♪The best is yet to come♪

1100
00:50:16,125 --> 00:50:18,274
♪The best is yet to come♪

1101
00:50:18,570 --> 00:50:19,984
♪Isn't it magical♪

1102
00:50:19,984 --> 00:50:22,196
♪Feeling uneasy,
yet no one's chasing me♪

1103
00:50:22,270 --> 00:50:24,624
♪Retreating step by step,
everything turning to ash♪

1104
00:50:24,624 --> 00:50:25,712
♪I'm silent, I'm roaring♪

1105
00:50:25,712 --> 00:50:29,163
♪This helplessness
keeps pushing me towards the cliff♪

1106
00:50:29,616 --> 00:50:31,890
♪Trembling legs
carry away a shattered soul♪

1107
00:50:32,304 --> 00:50:33,168
♪Who wants to be just a passerby♪

1108
00:50:33,168 --> 00:50:34,688
♪Isn't it magical♪
